<isis lang="en">
    <stitle>CF 500, CF 600 Suspension - Suspension System - General Information - Suspension Diagnosis and Testing
    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="test" graphiccount="0">
        <title>Suspension Diagnosis and Testing</title>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Inspection and Verification</title>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Road test.</para>
                <para>&#8226; Verify the customer's concern by performing a road test on a smooth road. If any
                    vibrations are apparent, refer to
                    <exhotlnk document="../S10/S10019.htm" bookname="S10019">Noise, Vibration and Harshness in
                        S10019</exhotlnk>.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Inspect tires.</para>
                <para>&#8226; Check the tire pressure with all normal loads in the vehicle and the tires cold; refer to
                    the vehicle certification (VC) label.
                </para>
                <para>&#8226; Verify that all tires are sized to specification. Refer to
                    <exhotlnk document="../S17/S17002.htm" bookname="S17002">Wheels and Tires in S17002</exhotlnk>.
                </para>
                <para>&#8226; Inspect the tires for incorrect wear and damage. Refer to
                    <exhotlnk document="../S17/S17002.htm" bookname="S17002">Wheels and Tires in S17002</exhotlnk>.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Inspect chassis and underbody.</para>
                <para>&#8226; Remove any excessive accumulation of mud, dirt or road deposits from the chassis and
                    underbody.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">Inspect for aftermarket equipment.</para>
                <para>&#8226; Check for aftermarket changes to the steering, suspension, wheel and tire components (such
                    as competition, heavy duty, etc.) The specifications shown in this manual do not apply to vehicles
                    equipped with aftermarket equipment.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <table id="t040007">
                <title>Visual Inspection Chart</title>
                <tgroup cols="1">
                    <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="0.84*"/>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Mechanical</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <randlist type="bullet">
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Front wheel bearing(s)</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose or damaged front or rear suspension components</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose, damaged or missing suspension fastener(s)</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose or damaged shackle(s)</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Restricted intake or exhaust</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Incorrect spring usage</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Damaged or sagging spring(s)</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Damaged or leaking shock absorber(s)</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Worn or damaged suspension bushing(s)</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose, worn or damaged steering system components</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Damaged axle components</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Damaged or loose kingpins (spindle pins)</para>
                                    </item>
                                </randlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">If an obvious cause for an observed or reported condition is found, correct the cause
                    (if possible) before proceeding to the next step.
                </para>
            </step1>
            <step1>
                <para count="1">If the fault is not visually evident, determine the symptom. Go to the Symptom Chart
                    below.
                </para>
            </step1>
        </svcsubproc>
        <svcsubproc>
            <title>Symptom Chart</title>
            <table id="t040008" tblwidth="pg-wide">
                <tgroup cols="3">
                    <colspec colname="col1" colwidth="0.90*"/>
                    <colspec colname="col2" colwidth="1.02*"/>
                    <colspec colname="col3" colwidth="1.07*"/>
                    <tbody>
                        <row>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Condition</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Possible Sources</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry align="center">
                                <para>
                                    <emph type="bold">Action</emph>
                                </para>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Dogtracking</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Excessive rear thrust angle.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Front or rear suspension components.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Drive axle damaged.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ADJUST as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSPECT the front and rear suspension systems. REPAIR or INSTALL new
                                            components as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension
                                            </hotlnk>
                                            or
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040212.xml" xrefid="x2040212">Rear
                                                Suspension</hotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REPAIR as necessary. REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S14/S14020.htm" bookname="S14020">Rear Drive
                                                Axle/Differential in S14020</exhotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Drift/pull</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Unequal tire pressure.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Excessive side-to-side difference in caster or camber.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Tire forces.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Unevenly loaded or overloaded vehicle.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Steering components.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Brake drag.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ADJUST tire pressure.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ADJUST as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ROTATE tires front to rear.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>NOTIFY the customer of incorrect vehicle loading.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S05/S05017.htm" bookname="S05017">Steering System in
                                                S05017.</exhotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S04/S04049.htm" bookname="S04049">Brake System in
                                                S04049.</exhotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Front bottoming or riding low</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Front spring(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Jounce bumper bracket or Front suspension bumper(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new front spring(s) as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension.
                                            </hotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new components as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension.
                                            </hotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Incorrect tire wear</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Incorrect tire pressure (rapid center rib or inner and outer edge wear).
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Excessive front or rear toe (rapid inner or outer edge wear) or Excessive
                                            negative or positive camber (rapid inner or outer edge wear).
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Tires out of balance (tires cupped or dished).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Kingpin (spindle pin) damaged.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ADJUST tire pressure.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ADJUST as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>BALANCE tires.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REPAIR as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension.
                                            </hotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Rear spring squeak</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Rear spring(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Shackle bushing(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new rear spring anti-squeak inserts.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new components as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Rough ride</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Shock absorber(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Spring(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new components as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new components as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension
                                            </hotlnk>
                                            or
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040212.xml" xrefid="x2040212">Rear
                                                Suspension</hotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Shimmy or wheel tramp</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose wheel nut(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose front suspension fasteners.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Front wheel bearing adjustment.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Wheel or tire concerns.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Springs or Kingpin (spindle pin) shims missing.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose, worn or damaged steering components.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Front wheel alignment.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>TIGHTEN to specification. REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S17/S17002.htm" bookname="S17002">Wheels and Tires in
                                                S17002
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>TIGHTEN to specification. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension.
                                            </hotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S10/S10019.htm" bookname="S10019">Noise, Vibration
                                                and Harshness in S10019.
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S17/S17002.htm" bookname="S17002">Wheels and Tires in
                                                S17002
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new components as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension
                                            </hotlnk>
                                            or
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040212.xml" xrefid="x2040212">Rear
                                                Suspension</hotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S05/S05017.htm" bookname="S05017">Steering System in
                                                S05017.
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ADJUST as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Sticky steering, poor returnability</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Steering components.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Front wheel alignment.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S05/S05017.htm" bookname="S05017">Steering System in
                                                S05017.
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ADJUST as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Steering wheel off-center</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Unequal front or rear toe settings (side-to-side).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Steering components.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ADJUST as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S05/S05017.htm" bookname="S05017">Steering System in
                                                S05017.
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Sway or roll</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Overloaded, unevenly or incorrectly loaded vehicle.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose wheel nut(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Shock absorber(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose stabilizer assembly.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Worn stabilizer assembly bushing(s) or Worn spring(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>NOTIFY the customer of incorrect vehicle loading.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>TIGHTEN to specification. REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S17/S17002.htm" bookname="S17002">Wheels and Tires in
                                                S17002
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new components as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>TIGHTEN to specification. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension
                                            </hotlnk>
                                            or
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040212.xml" xrefid="x2040212">Rear
                                                Suspension</hotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new components as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension
                                            </hotlnk>
                                            or
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040212.xml" xrefid="x2040212">Rear
                                                Suspension</hotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Vehicle leans to one side</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Unevenly loaded or overloaded vehicle.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Front or rear suspension components.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Spring(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Incorrect ride height. Lateral tilt out of specification.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>NOTIFY the customer of incorrect vehicle loading.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSPECT the front and rear suspension systems. REPAIR or INSTALL new
                                            components as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension
                                            </hotlnk>
                                            or
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040212.xml" xrefid="x2040212">Rear
                                                Suspension</hotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new components as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension
                                            </hotlnk>
                                            or
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040212.xml" xrefid="x2040212">Rear
                                                Suspension</hotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSPECT the rear suspension system. REPAIR or INSTALL new rear suspension
                                            components as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension
                                            </hotlnk>
                                            or
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040212.xml" xrefid="x2040212">Rear
                                                Suspension</hotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Vibration/noise</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Tires and wheel concerns, Wheel bearings, Wheel hubs, Brake components,
                                            Suspension components, or Steering components.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S10/S10019.htm" bookname="S10019">Noise, Vibration
                                                and Harshness in S10019.
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <entry>
                                <para>Wander</para>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Unevenly loaded or overloaded vehicle.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose, worn or damaged front wheel bearing(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose, worn or damaged suspension component(s).</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Loose suspension fasteners.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Steering components.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>Wheel alignment (excessive total front toe out).</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                            <entry>
                                <seqlist>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>NOTIFY the customer of incorrect vehicle loading.</para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S10/S10019.htm" bookname="S10019">Noise, Vibration
                                                and Harshness in S10019.
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>INSTALL new components as necessary. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension.
                                            </hotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>TIGHTEN to specification. REFER to
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040111.xml" xrefid="x2040111">Front Suspension
                                            </hotlnk>
                                            or
                                            <hotlnk document="s03014_X2040212.xml" xrefid="x2040212">Rear
                                                Suspension</hotlnk>.
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>REFER to
                                            <exhotlnk document="../S05/S05017.htm" bookname="S05017">Steering System in
                                                S05017.
                                            </exhotlnk>
                                        </para>
                                    </item>
                                    <item>
                                        <para>ADJUST as necessary.</para>
                                    </item>
                                </seqlist>
                            </entry>
                        </row>
                    </tbody>
                </tgroup>
            </table>
        </svcsubproc>
